title: VIRAL MOMENT: Senate erupts in LAUGHTER at Trump lawyer during impeachment hearing
author: Forbes Breaking News
description: VIRAL MOMENT: Senate erupts in laughter when Trump lawyer calls for depositions in his office in Philadelphia: "I don't know why you're laughing!"

localize.description: VIRAL MOMENT。特朗普律师在费城办公室要求取证时，参议院爆发了笑声。"我不知道你为什么笑！"
localize.title: VIRAL MOMENT。参议院在弹劾听证会上对特朗普律师大笑不止

localize.description: VIRAL MOMENT。特朗普律師在費城辦公室要求取證時，參議院爆發了笑聲。"我不知道你爲什麼笑！"
localize.title: VIRAL MOMENT。參議院在彈劾聽證會上對特朗普律師大笑不止
